{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this world, the cat tribe is universally disliked by all living beings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A silver-haired woman is seeking a way to coexist with the cat tribe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This story is about their \u201clittle adventure to realize the world they envision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201d The story is heartwarming throughout and is aimed at a wide range of players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25a0 Everything is made up of small elements </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is composed of \u201clittle\u201d elements in every aspect. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can enjoy small maps, small discoveries, and small stories in a short amount of time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25a0 Growth System</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not only do characters have levels, but weapons and armor also have growth elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Especially for weapons, equipping and fighting with them will level them up just like the characters, adding more fun to the battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25a0 Collection Elements </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many treasures and animals are hidden in places that are not immediately obvious, allowing you to explore and find them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each map also contains materials that can be collected to craft and enhance weapons and armor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have an urgent matter, please send a DM to @ArtWorkers_0511 (X account).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cControls\u201d </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I strongly recommend using an Xbox controller. The controls for mouse and keyboard are as follows:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A, S, D, W (\u2190\u2193\u2192\u2191): Move character/cursor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Z, Space, Return: Investigate, Attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">X, Backspace: Cancel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Esc: Open Menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1~3: Use Skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only the camera rotation uses the mouse.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821230/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727416532","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821230/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1727416532","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821230/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727416532","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821230/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727416532","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this world, the cat tribe is universally disliked by all living beings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A silver-haired woman is seeking a way to coexist with the cat tribe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This story is about their \u201clittle adventure to realize the world they envision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201d The story is heartwarming throughout and is aimed at a wide range of players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25a0 Everything is made up of small elements </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is composed of \u201clittle\u201d elements in every aspect. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can enjoy small maps, small discoveries, and small stories in a short amount of time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25a0 Growth System</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not only do characters have levels, but weapons and armor also have growth elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Especially for weapons, equipping and fighting with them will level them up just like the characters, adding more fun to the battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u25a0 Collection Elements </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many treasures and animals are hidden in places that are not immediately obvious, allowing you to explore and find them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each map also contains materials that can be collected to craft and enhance weapons and armor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have an urgent matter, please send a DM to @ArtWorkers_0511 (X account).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cControls\u201d </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I strongly recommend using an Xbox controller. The controls for mouse and keyboard are as follows:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A, S, D, W (\u2190\u2193\u2192\u2191): Move character/cursor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Z, Space, Return: Investigate, Attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">X, Backspace: Cancel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Esc: Open Menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1~3: Use Skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only the camera rotation uses the mouse.</p>","developers":["Asuka Watanabe"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821230/header.jpg?t=1727416532","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257050459,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257050459/movie480.mp4?t=1724911694","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257050459/movie_max.mp4?t=1724911694"},"name":"EN preview1","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257050459/movie.293x165.jpg?t=17